          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The Shreveport City Council has been debating about outfitting the police department with high-speed muscle cars. Originally, the proposal was to buy 4-6 Dodge Challenger Hellcats. After some debate among the members of the council, that was changed to 8 Dodge Chargers, we’re assuming not Hellcats, but maybe Scat Packs? The whole thing is pretty controversial.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
